label: State Pride: An oration delivered before the Calliopean and Polytechnic Societies of the State Military School, at Charleston on the 5th April, 1860.
description: This is a typewritten version of the oration entitled "State Pride" delivered by Hon. William D. Porter to the Calliopean and Polytechnic Societies of the State Military School in 1860. State government and its relation to federal government is discussed.
